{
  "stem": "17135.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Especially the little ones, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she could find the time to be in-- in-- in-- in the business.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was-- she was loving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even my father was not that strict.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to-- all children went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the three brothers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The oldest, the second, and me went to gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were at-- at the age already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my sister, Elly, went to lyceum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To the best of my knowledge, she was only 10 years-- she went, 2 or 2 and 1/2 years she went.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Until 1938, where we all were thrown out of school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we were allowed to go to-- to the-- to high school, which was unusual, because we were considered Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we would have been Germans, they would have thrown us out earlier.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- for some reason, that is not very logical, the Nazis, in order to maintain good relations with foreign countries, allowed Jews to go to public high schools if they were foreign citizens.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If we would-- the German Jews-- I remember, I had in my class, two boys-- they were German Jews-- in 1936, after the Nuremberg Laws came out, after the Olympics, they were thrown out of school.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not allowed, anymore, to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- so I was Jewish, but I was considered a foreign citizen-- or my parents were foreign citizens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They allowed us to stay in school until Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my god, and how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a frightening experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That really-- the Kristallnacht-- was, so to speak, I would say, the general rehearsal of the Nazis for the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It really was.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
